ation for a specific platform at compile-time. It also does only select\nthe architecture targeted by the JIT, which should result in slightly lower\ncompilation times on every platform, and lower binary sizes too.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D22280", "files": ["js/src/rust/Cargo.toml", "js/src/rust/moz.build", "js/src/rust/shared/Cargo.toml", "js/src/wasm/cranelift/Cargo.toml", "toolkit/library/gtest/rust/Cargo.toml", "toolkit/library/rust/Cargo.toml", "toolkit/library/rust/gkrust-features.mozbuild", "toolkit/library/rust/shared/Cargo.toml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "dbd1b0222c6f9f2f43a4bed4f0c8d4f262d23b45", "parents": ["cf114035c79fa00872568b863ef84c24ad8e7de2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matt Woodrow \u003cmwoodrow@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1518524 - Don't try to restore the previous FrameLayerBuilder after a transaction since it should always be nullptr anyway. r=miko\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D21879", "files": ["layout/painting/nsDisplayList.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3ee7abf6d43275fe1d936df32a40bf010450d62d", "parents": ["dbd1b0222c6f9f2f43a4bed4f0c8d4f262d23b45"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Gurzau Raul \u003crgurzau@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge autoland to mozilla-central. a=merge", "files": ["js/src/builtin/Array.cpp", "js/src/jit/CodeGenerator.cpp", "js/src/vm/ArrayObject-inl.h", "js/src/vm/Interpreter.cpp", "js/src/vm/NativeObject-inl.h", "js/src/vm/ProxyObject.cpp", "js/src/vm/UnboxedObject.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "6f32ec5e62e3a3b20d2c16e13f963981603768df", "parents": ["0bf136f3ac45ce5e1c5d76c9c89d2fed6d15d0c4", "3ee7abf6d43275fe1d936df32a40bf010450d62d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Julian Seward \u003cjseward@acm.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1533204 - Crash [@ js::jit::CompileRuntime::mainContextPtr] with asm.js.  r=j