 Skupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1535026 - [marionette] 'mach marionette-test' should force e10s disabled for Fennec. r=ato\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D23401", "files": ["testing/marionette/doc/Testing.md", "testing/marionette/mach_commands.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0607c72b4d88f2481152837fb94000b383e051dc", "parents": ["4905cca9fa818ebcab585fb7c988e685e0b7c551"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Christoph Kerschbaumer \u003cckerschb@christophkerschbaumer.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1530854: Always create CSP on Principal so the explicit CSP in the nsISHEntry holds a reference to the potentially dynamically modified CSP in case of a meta CSP. r=bzbarsky\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D21919", "files": ["caps/nsScriptSecurityManager.cpp", "dom/base/Document.cpp", "dom/security/nsCSPContext.cpp", "dom/security/test/csp/test_data_doc_ignore_meta_csp.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "30b70cd830631e09d18fafe5937fdbc4ed4b1134", "parents": ["0607c72b4d88f2481152837fb94000b383e051dc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrei Lazar \u003candrei.a.lazar@softvision.ro\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1534207 Search Widget missing TELEMETRY probe for searches initiated r=petru\n\nAdded a telemetry probe (unique source value) to allow data science to measure percentage of searches initiated from the widget.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D22956", "files": ["mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/BrowserApp.java", "mobile/android/docs/uitelemetry.rst", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/TelemetryContract.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2c24099776a7c46fa4e764984901e386f5d83fd5", "parents": ["30b70cd830631e09d18fafe5937fdbc4ed4b1134"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Eden Chuang \u003cechuang@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1472307 - Implement delay update mechanism in ServiceWorkerRegistrationProxy. r=asuth\n\n1. Add a new private member class DelayedUpdateCallback in\n   ServiceWorkerRegistrationProxy for handling the deley time up.\n\n2. Modify the lambda function in ServiceWorkerRegistrationProxy::Update(). Get\n   the update delay time at first. If the delay time does not equal zero. create\n   a timer and a timer callback(DelayedUpdateCallback) to perform the delay\n   update. Otherwise execute update directly.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D17358", "files": ["dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerRegistrationProxy.cpp", "dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerRegistrationProxy.h", "dom/serviceworkers/test/test_self_update_worker.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e9e31edcc25a93b88e667ffa8d182d8c44a00310", "parents": ["2c24099776a7c46fa4e764984901e386f5d83fd5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Syeda Asra Arshia Qadri \u003casra.qadri@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1469774 - Error this.pageListener is undefined in AboutPrivateBrowsingHandler.jsm r=johannh\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D23295", "files": ["browser/components/about/AboutPrivateBrowsingHandler.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5da37483c3e2278f7adca24137f33c8c49fc6e63", "parents": ["e9e31edcc25a93b88e667ffa8d182d8c44a00310"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Christoph Kerschbaumer \u003cckerschb@christophkerschbaumer.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1532207: Do not query the CSP from the principal within LoadFrame, but rather do not even set the Principal if it does not override the CSP within nsContentUtils::GetAttrTriggeringPrincipal. r=bzbarsky\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D22121", "files": ["dom/base/nsContentUtils.cpp", "dom/base/nsFrameLoader.cpp", "dom/base/nsFrameLoader.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f1