ng added to the queue.\n\nDepends on D23528\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D23529", "files": ["mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/LauncherActivity.java", "mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/tabqueue/TabQueueHelper.java", "mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/tabqueue/TabQueueService.java", "mobile/android/base/locales/en-US/android_strings.dtd", "mobile/android/base/strings.xml.in"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "36132f5347e8b31f4fe5b28d0bd182f6fe606237", "parents": ["069dea6b6bc5b0b4bc43d00e3b6e55c7b25ae245"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nicolas Chevobbe \u003cnchevobbe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1535305 - Guard this.jsterm access in webconsole-ui.js. r=Honza.\n\nDepending on the load, this.jsterm might not be\nset when switching to the console panel, and can\ncause a crash (blank tab).\nThis patch checks that this.jsterm exists before\ntaking further actions.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D23511", "files": ["devtools/client/webconsole/webconsole-ui.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ad59be7ee0c20a42f70989bcce84308fdd66619a", "parents": ["36132f5347e8b31f4fe5b28d0bd182f6fe606237"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Christoph Kerschbaumer \u003cckerschb@christophkerschbaumer.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1534971: Add helper function within CSP to check if two CSPs are equal. r=jkt\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D23567", "files": ["caps/nsScriptSecurityManager.cpp", "docshell/base/nsDocShell.cpp", "dom/security/nsCSPContext.cpp", "dom/security/nsCSPContext.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6343f4a4d75eca45559003206bce65c8c3c14f3e", "parents": ["ad59be7ee0c20a42f70989bcce84308fdd66619a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Byron Campen [:bwc] \u003cdocfaraday@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1531811 - Part 1: Remove onremovestream from RTC