indow dimensions and make the broken path an error instead.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D23323\n", "files": ["testing/marionette/reftest.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "95f1a7ff5760ed51b90ede77e65e98c5ffc629de", "parents": ["ad53fdccd298a17c68bb72c3fb24aa890387765b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brindusan Cristian \u003ccbrindusan@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out 201 changesets (bug 1530837, bug 1529206, bug 1528232, bug 1530834, bug 1528032, bug 1530831, bug 1528237, bug 1529242, bug 1529821, bug 1530839, bug 1509034, bug 1527222, bug 1528705, bug 1530812, bug 1528266, bug 1528274, bug 1529038, bug 1464538, bug 1531331, bug 1531337, bug 1529734, bug 1528888, bug 1528887, bug 1527719, bug 1528711, bug 1527514, bug 1527981, bug 1528927, bug 1528949, bug 1531007, bug 1528736, bug 1531372, bug 1528732, bug 1530825, bug 1529061, bug 1528204, bug 1527487, bug 1528741, bug 1527961, bug 1527353, bug 1529208, bug 1527643, bug 1529244, bug 1526836, bug 1529740, bug 1527540, bug 1486514, bug 1526863, bug 1528719, bug 1529749, bug 1528954, bug 1528721, bug 1527560, bug 1526275, bug 1528894, bug 1527212, bug 1531341, bug 1529756, bug 1527584, bug 1527634, bug 1528728, bug 1527474, bug 1529438, bug 1528919, bug 1531365, bug 1528853, bug 1528726, bug 1529430, bug 1529341, bug 1529263, bug 1529459, bug 1528058, bug 1528722, bug 1528746, bug 1528211, bug 1529092, bug 1528152, bug 1529059, bug 1529229, bug 1529752, bug 1529052, bug 1529712, bug 1529055, bug 1529717, bug 1528700, bug 1528862, bug 1526647, bug 1529814, bug 1528868, bug 1529810, bug 1531069, bug 1527478, bug 1529462, bug 1528716, bug 1528828, bug 1531256, bug 1529426, bug 1531357, bug 1531064, bug 1529156, bug 1529724, bug 1529726, bug 1527483, bug 1527638, bug 1526801, bug 1528229, bug 1530852, bug 1529080, bug 1528109, bug 1528029, bug 1529435, bug 1527669, bug 1526881, bug 1529315, bug 1528023, bug 1527661, bug 1529046, bug 15262