ad7ac51543dc135495d8f110188"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Rakina Zata Amni \u003crakina@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529315 [wpt PR 15474] - Mark shadow trees for style collection update when inserted to document, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nMark shadow trees for style collection update when inserted to document\n\nWhen we attach shadow trees with non-empty |adoptedStyleSheets|, we\nshould update the active style sheet collection for that tree scope.\nOtherwise, if there are no other stylesheets for that tree scope,\nwe will never mark the tree scope as dirty and thus have incorrect\nstyle calculation for that tree scope.\n\nBug: 933578\nChange-Id: Id7229b05440a51ac8e5d55570ed030b8cfb707d2\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/1477623\nReviewed-by: Kent Tamura \u003ctkent@chromium.org\u003e\nCommit-Queue: Rakina Zata Amni \u003crakina@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#633666}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 7266a4200f24ade6c91608ab05a936770c92e2f0\nwpt-pr: 15474\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/cssom/CSSStyleSheet-constructable.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "258fdb4dac181a03048494d63d00784f4066edfe", "parents": ["81ace099679c1783d6711a39e7d9ee6d3585ae7c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529315 [wpt PR 15474] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 15474\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/css/cssom/CSSStyleSheet-constructable.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "911198c7a3fcd3f3958fa208173eec2af89df827", "parents": ["258fdb4dac181a03048494d63d00784f4066edfe"], "tags": []}, {"author": "jugglinmike \u003cmike@mikepennisi.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529244 [wpt PR 15472] - [wptrunner] Remove unused method, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\n[wptrunner] Remove unused method (#15472)\n\n`after_conect` is a misnomer for the `after_connect` method of the\ngeneric `Protocol` class.\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 048fff6e501c70fdcd2181bf04b3194afe64daa1\nwpt-pr: 15472\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/tools/wptrunner/wptrunner/executors/executorselenium.py", "testing/web-platform/tests/tools/wptrunner/wptrunner/executors/executorwebdriver.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e20cba1999ba07671c6e7ee7762eeaf112fbecaf", "parents": ["911198c7a3fcd3f3958fa208173eec2af89df827"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Philip J\u00e4genstedt \u003cphilip@foolip.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529426 [wpt PR 15477] - [Azure Pipelines] Remove the wpt.fyi hook (no longer needed), a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\n[Azure Pipelines] Remove the wpt.fyi hook (no longer needed) (#15477)\n\nAs found in https://github.com/web-platform-tests/wpt.fyi/issues/1130,\nthis hook is no longer needed, check runs are created also for\nscheduled builds on Azure Pipelines.\n--\n\nwpt-commits: f3b13634825af90ecb94398349add2e20fade639\nwpt-pr: 15477\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/.azure-pipelines.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bde440dca3faddab96fdb4d85a38c45b7afa1a29", "parents": ["e20cba1999ba07671c6e7ee7762eeaf112fbecaf"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Paul Meyer \u003cpaulmeyer@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529156 [wpt PR 15305] - Add testdriver support for generate_test_report WebDriver command., a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nAdd testdriver support for generate_test_report WebDriver command.\n\nAlso adds Reporting API tests which utilize this command.\n\n--\nfix lint errors\n\n--\nAdd comments to tests\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 5109698f5a9b61797c86fda8000baeb0e701f3f1, 49f474206a2374f3da136f3ddb62cb85ea5c5532, c0a12dae123c560ef835c19e166a253e44275c80\nwpt-pr: 15305\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/reporting/bufferSize.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/reporting/disconnect.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/reporting/generateTestReport.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/reporting/nestedReport.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/reporting/order.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/resources/testdriver.js", "testing/web-platform/tests/tools/wptrunner/wptrunner/executors/base.py", "testing/web-platform/tests/tools/wptrunner/wptrunner/executors/executorwebdriver.py", "testing/web-platform/tests/tools/wptrunner/wptrunner/executors/protocol.py", "testing/web-platform/tests/tools/wptrunner/wptrunner/testdriver-extra.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a7fb7ac01c01b3dd651e827a2f8e1118f0ade3c2", "parents": ["bde440dca3faddab96fdb4d85a38c45b7afa1a29"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529156 [wpt PR 15305] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 15305\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/reporting/bufferSize.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/reporting/disconnect.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/reporting/generateTestReport.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/reporting/nestedReport.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/reporting/order.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "53d055724690f5348ff99e07c2f1557f2e6c5b72", "parents": ["a7fb7ac01c01b3dd651e827a2f8e1118f0ade3c2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike West \u003cmkwst@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1528274 [wpt PR 15418] - Sec-CH-UA: Send only the major version by default., a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nSec-CH-UA: Send only the major version by default.\n\nRather than sending a `Sec-CH-UA` header containing the full version\nnumber by default (e.g. \"Chromium 99.0.1232.12\"), send only the major\nversion (e.g. \"Chromium 99\").\n\nThis does not effect the value of `UserAgent.version` obtained from\n`navigator.getUserAgent()`, but only the HTTP request header.\n\nBug: 928669\nChange-Id: I074e244a3918b0bdab4453c2f56dc737c506f732\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/1475438\nReviewed-by: Jochen Eisinger \u003cjochen@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Tarun Bansal \u003ctbansal@chromium.org\u003e\nCommit-Queue: Mike West \u003cmkwst@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#633726}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: f70ff91fce2695f4303075b45eb8660f7a8d6508\nwpt-pr: 15418\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/client-hints/resources/sec-ch-ua.py", "testing/web-platform/tests/client-hints/sec-ch-ua.http.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/client-hints/sec-ch-ua.https.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9ba789d8e8d3c6fa7d6ba36d3fff09411e311e9c", "parents": ["53d055724690f5348ff99e07c2f1557f2e6c5b72"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1528274 [wpt PR 15418] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 15418\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/client-hints/sec-ch-ua.https.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fabf03c3df32ee82b484792597ca20cba816ecf5", "parents": ["9ba789d8e8d3c6fa7d6ba36d3fff09411e311e9c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brandon Jones \u003cbajones@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529206 [wpt PR 14804] - Enforce active lifetime of XRFrame objects, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nEnforce active lifetime of XRFrame objects\n\nReland of https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/1343065\nIncorporates fixes made by jacde@chromium.org (Thanks!)\n\nDeactivates XRFrame objects once the relevant callback returns, which\ncauses future calls to the object methods to throw an exception.\n\nBug: 906842\nChange-Id: Ib635f56ed28b728434a08347b9d9fb98d1ecd694\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/1363836\nCommit-Queue: Brandon Jones \u003cbajones@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Klaus Weidner \u003cklausw@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#633845}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 91b1effe848fac6e73a203037fc333b0fff3174d\nwpt-pr: 14804\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/webxr/xrFrame_lifetime.https.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1244fe26b18d5d196d341382479f9def243b5f4d", "parents": ["fabf03c3df32ee82b484792597ca20cba816ecf5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529206 [wpt PR 14804] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 14804\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/webxr/xrFrame_lifetime.https.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e61e1c0300f2259a30b40aa357ea522aee712cbc", "parents": ["1244fe26b18d5d196d341382479f9def243b5f4d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Darwin Huang \u003chuangdarwin@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1529229 [wpt PR 15470] - Async Clipboard: Make test naming more clear, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nAsync Clipboard: Make test naming more clear\n\n- Test messages and errors had confusing/outdated typenames, so this CL aims to\nupdate them and make them more consistent.\n- No test logic changes.\n\nBug: 896479\nChange-Id: I68726a63e6d7f6c8f964b902c5fa9dbc691787f5\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/1478296\nCommit-Queue: Darwin Huang \u003chuangdarwin@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Victor Costan \u003cpwnall@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#634005}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: b6d9f766aaea899da6b1c6d585f2e68f996a3c39\nwpt-pr: 15470\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/clipboard-apis/async-navigator-clipboard-basics.https.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/clipboard-apis/async-write-blobtext-read-blobtext-manual.https.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/clipboard-apis/async-write-blobtext-read-text-manual.https.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/clipboard-apis/async-write