shi Horo \u003choro@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1527961 [wpt PR 15372] - Implement Signed Exchange reporting for distributors, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nImplement Signed Exchange reporting for distributors\n\nThis CL implements Signed Exchange reporting for distributors.\nSpec: https://github.com/WICG/webpackage/pull/374\n\nThis CL has two success test cases only.\nI will add more failure test cases in another CL.\n\nBug: 910516\nChange-Id: I31a6e629073970e03a93d2379be1ae63ef6adf6b\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/1468855\nCommit-Queue: Tsuyoshi Horo \u003choro@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Christian Dullweber \u003cdullweber@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Kinuko Yasuda \u003ckinuko@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Kouhei Ueno \u003ckouhei@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Kunihiko Sakamoto \u003cksakamoto@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Eric Orth \u003cericorth@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#634161}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 66dbfd0ae579135db73772c534879c51f6dbc674\nwpt-pr: 15372\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/network-error-logging/support/nel.sub.js", "testing/web-platform/tests/network-error-logging/support/report.py", "testing/web-platform/tests/signed-exchange/reporting/sxg-reporting-navigation-ok.tentative.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/signed-exchange/reporting/sxg-reporting-prefetch-ok.tentative.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/signed-exchange/resources/sxg-util.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5f4503098f271c69d34c5a028f5a5eb909859e79", "parents": ["5fcf15c3c730e29f844986f09e3f569a7dac24d9"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1527961 [wpt PR 15372] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 15372\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/signed-exchange/reporting/sxg-reporting-navigation-ok.tentative.html.ini", "tes