leuzu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1537566 - Fix brightness of selected netmonitor rows; r=fvsch a=pascalc\n\nSummary: Remove unnecessary css\n\nReviewers: fvsch\n\nReviewed By: fvsch\n\nBug #: 1537566\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D24339", "files": ["devtools/client/netmonitor/src/assets/styles/RequestList.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3bfd427973deaf41b48791a69db91f29b67d0460", "parents": ["de506694d256d9518bc4f1354791898a21bc4711"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Narcis Beleuzu \u003cnbeleuzu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1536264 - Only reset color / background / text-shadow for active options. r=jaws,mconley a=pascalc\n\nSummary:\n\nOtherwise you see font changes when hovering, which is not really desirable.\n\nReviewers: jaws, mconley\n\nReviewed By: jaws\n\nBug #: 1536264\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D24116", "files": ["toolkit/modules/SelectParentHelper.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9d77f46fc075dcbfeb83fa55c39245f93bc2f2d5", "parents": ["3bfd427973deaf41b48791a69db91f29b67d0460"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Narcis Beleuzu \u003cnbeleuzu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1534447 - Add application menu item to show Logins & Passwords. r=Gijs a=pascalc\n\nReviewers: Gijs\n\nReviewed By: Gijs\n\nSubscribers: MattN\n\nBug #: 1534447\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D23737", "files": ["browser/components/customizableui/content/panelUI.inc.xul", "browser/themes/shared/menupanel.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bda705ea201f2bbc11f260d7691ad1c69029c424", "parents": ["9d77f46fc075dcbfeb83fa55c39245f93bc2f2d5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Narcis Beleuzu \u003cnbeleuzu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1534447 - Replace login and login-detailed icon with new icon. r=Gijs a=pascalc\n\nReviewers: Gijs\n\nRevi