, "files": ["js/src/jit-test/tests/basic/testTypedArrayInit.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0f095fa12e03248e1e1eef9e1f6a3624ff103887", "parents": ["e32e741e525fcad5c7d0e2a827c7e810995bb473"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Hiroyuki Ikezoe \u003chikezoe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1141387 - Set image.animation_mode=none to avoid the animated GIF is advanced to the next frame. r=heycam, a=test-only\n\nThe animated GIF in background-blending-image-color-gif.html has two animation\nframes, the one is a red rectangle, the other is a green rectangle.  The reftest\nis supposed to take the snapshot during the time where the animation frame is\nthe red rectangle (the first frame) and the frame duration is 1000ms.  So if we\ntake over 1000ms there for some reasons, say on slow platforms, before taking\nthe snapshot, the reftet fails.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D24843", "files": ["layout/reftests/css-blending/reftest.list"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9174ce9e9471a036ee409eb674a1f26799be289a", "parents": ["0f095fa12e03248e1e1eef9e1f6a3624ff103887"], "tags": []}], "date": 1554126907, "git_changesets": [null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10972": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nbr -\u003e 35909367f361\ncy -\u003e 3752651a3077\nes-AR -\u003e bba9df9f5a16\nfy-NL -\u003e a40c51c8a6ff\nsv-SE -\u003e cdbb1cf563da\nvi -\u003e bdc0abe99093\nzh-TW -\u003e c82668d2cd21", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "367e131a8231074f44f535557ebca9dfe4f43082", "parents": ["9174ce9e9471a036ee409eb674a1f26799be289a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n 