"git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c59ea80a07d69ed9b09e5b007f3bb4c276418fb2", "parents": ["f8ee8d095defcc30b9243907b8d00110d21e74c7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\ndsb -\u003e 2c1f7ddbcf5f\nel -\u003e cf782860c601\ngd -\u003e af93690296ad\nhsb -\u003e c7c975ebd065\npl -\u003e 92dab0c2876b\nzh-CN -\u003e f7192f85048d", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4dd5a57324894245168590868b807ceedba2af6b", "parents": ["c59ea80a07d69ed9b09e5b007f3bb4c276418fb2"], "tags": []}], "date": 1555772431, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "11121": {"changesets": [{"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1545842 - Downgrade RestyleManager assertions to DIAGNOSTIC_ASSERT in beta. r=tnikkel a=pascalc\n\nSummary:\nThe only case where we know that this assert breaks right now is in\nnsIconChannel.\n\nnsIconChannel is used for moz-icon://, which is not exposed to content.\n\nSo it doesn't seem to be easy to potentially get into a broken state that\ncontent could exploit, and thus crashes in release may be a bit excessive.\n\nDowngrade the assertion for now.\n\nReviewers: tnikkel\n\nReviewed By: tnikkel\n\nBug #: 1545842\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D28248", "files": ["layout/base/RestyleManager.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bdd03a2c4e54d9bd9f6822ab5bef134d11d67f90", "parents": ["4dd5a57324894245168590868b807ceedba2af6b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Lee Salzman \u003clsalzman@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1544188 - check cleartype level for WR DWrite fonts. r=jfkthame a=pascalc\n\nReviewers: jfkthame\n\nReviewed By: jfkthame\n\nBug #: 1544188\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D27563", "files": ["gfx/2d/ScaledFontDWrite.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a3857b3191a4c9b4676ab5ff603e09c39546c23a", "parents": ["bdd03a2c4e54d9bd9f6822ab5bef134d11d67f90"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brian Grinstead \u003cbgrinstead@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1543828 - Use \u003cbdi\u003e inside video controls content. r=Gijs a=pascalc\n\nReviewers: Gijs\n\nReviewed By: Gijs\n\nSubscribers: Kwan\n\nBug #: 1543828\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D27757", "files": ["toolkit/content/widgets/videocontrols.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6cd36394e2aeaea04ad1978e7131ac86da02f1f1", "parents": ["a3857b3191a4c9b4676ab5ff603e09c39546c23a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Petru Lingurar \u003cpetru.lingurar@softvision.ro\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1543680 - Set playbackState as playing when entering in PiP mode. r=JanH a=pascalc\n\nSummary:\nplaybackState's default value is PlaybackState.STOPPED.\nWe can only enter PiP mode if media is playing but we don't save this playing\nstate.\nIf the user hasn't done anything to change this, like pause-play, when we check\nthe playbackState in BrowserApp to know to force fullscreen if still playing\nwe will not do so because the state is PlaybackState.STOPPED.\n\nReviewers: JanH\n\nReviewed By: JanH\n\nSubscribers: jya\n\nBug #: 1543680\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D27935", "files": ["mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/media/PictureInPictureController.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2d12891a1a5493bac5886af3ede2db14b30a1ee6", "parents": ["6cd36394e2aeaea04ad1978e7131ac86da02f1f1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Farre \u003cfarre@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1541038 - Part 1: Sync a BrowsingContext to it's groups. r=nika a=pascalc\n\nReviewers: nika\n\nReviewed By: nika\n\nSubscribers: reviewbot\n\nBug #: 1541038\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D27317", "files": ["dom/ipc/ContentParent.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b476772da6b0bcb6331b98cedfbdc3faae72388f", "parents": ["2d12891a1a5493bac5886af3ede2db14b30a1ee6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Vlad Baicu \u003cvlad.baicu@softvision.ro\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1527666 - Handle long back press manually only on Android N. r=petru a=pascalc\n\nSummary:\nOn versions \u003e= N all long back presses we're handled manually in onKeyDown\nand onKeyUp which could lead to certain complications. I have changed it\nonly for Android N where onKeyLongPress does not trigger as it should.\n\nReviewers: petru\n\nReviewed By: petru\n\nBug #: 1527666\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D28037", "files": ["mobile/android/base/AppConstants.java.in", "mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/BrowserApp.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "05d12183776b26907ebacbc9b0bbf282e148cc1a", "parents": ["b476772da6b0bcb6331b98cedfbdc3faae72388f"], "tags": []}], "date": 1555806284, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "nbeleuzu@mozilla.com"}, "11122": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nel -\u003e 781a08d7a35f\nen-GB -\u003e 6bf5c7f5819d\nhr -\u003e 91c23c12c8e9\nka -\u003e 4ab6a2e17e29\nkk -\u003e 6567e6761984\npt-BR -\u003e 0321c0d4b1a6\npt-PT -\u003e da6ed22d2ac4\nru -\u003e f2dbce29d5ec\ntrs -\u003e 54ea558083f7\nvi -\u003e 6492b71172b3\nzh-CN -\u003e 7be1faa83069", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "53aff488b7f62eef3f90d7a7f81290374ccd2a45", "parents": ["05d12183776b26907ebacbc9b0bbf282e148cc1a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u00