BIRD670b3_2019050701_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Bug 1530207 - fix crash  [@ InvalidArrayIndex_CRASH | mozilla::a11y::Accessible::InsertChildAt]. r=surkov a=jorgk DONTBUILD\n\nFor XULTreeAccessible, the ChildCount() is not only the mChildren, so check mChildren directly to make sure we stay within bounds\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D27553", "files": ["accessible/generic/DocAccessible.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3de7bd6c47c061ed65ad61e74e8873faf83fa5a1", "parents": ["fe6ddfaa325f8e9b57b134cd5ff48753726b8aff"], "tags": []}], "date": 1557259538, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "mozilla@jorgk.com"}, "11250": {"changesets": [{"author": "Chris Pearce \u003ccpearce@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1548410 - Disable DXVA on Qualcomm WoA drivers. r=mattwoodrow a=pascalc\n\nThis driver version is known to have busg which cause the output of green\nframes from the decoder, and to cause BSODs.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D29603", "files": ["widget/windows/GfxInfo.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "79e9a8ef0735ae3a27531a09a54bc3b2771766a6", "parents": ["7c01984d0300b910f42e1abd4c57ad5d51539451"], "tags": []}], "date": 1557262588, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ncsoregi@mozilla.com"}, "11251": {"changesets": [{"author": "Haik Aftandilian \u003chaftandilian@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546544 - Enable TCSM r=asuth,spohl,mccr8 a=abillings", "files": ["netwerk/base/ProxyAutoConfig.cpp", "netwerk/base/moz.build", "security/sandbox/mac/SandboxPolicies.h", "toolkit/xre/moz.build", "xpcom/base/CycleCollectedJSRuntime.cpp", "xpcom/base/nsMacUtilsImpl.cpp", "xpcom/base/nsMacUtilsImpl.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d52fac94f5077ee49700efe646b67a613761cda9", "parents": ["79e9a8ef0735ae3a27531a09a54bc3b2771766a6"], "tags": []}], "date": 1557355005, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "asasaki@mozil